OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FThe US men's hockey team received a
OL,8,Ftwo-minute standing ovation at Donald
OL,9,FTrump's State of the Union address on
OL,10,FTuesday night after beating Canada to
OL,11,Fwin gold at the Winter Olympics.
OL,13,FThe women's team also won gold, but
OL,14,Fwere nowhere to be seen after they
OL,15,Fdeclined the US president's invitation.
OL,17,FIt comes amid controversy surrounding
OL,18,FFBI Director Kash Patel's celebrations
OL,19,Fwith the men's team and backlash to
OL,20,Fcomments the US president made about
OL,21,Fthe women's team.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
