OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FWhat happened and why has it become so
OL,8,Fcontroversial? ITV News explains.
OL,10,FWhat happened at the Games?
OL,12,FThe men's and women's US teams won
OL,13,Fgold at the Winter Olympics, both
OL,14,Fhaving beaten Canada to take the top
OL,15,Fspot.
OL,17,FBoth teams also won 2-1 in games that
OL,18,Fran into overtime. The men won for the
OL,19,Ffirst time in 46 years, while the
OL,20,Fwomen last won in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
