OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FHow did the US president react to the
OL,8,Fvictories?
OL,10,FAfter the men's victory, a video that
OL,11,Fcirculated on social media appeared to
OL,12,Fshow Trump congratulating the team on
OL,13,Ftheir achievement and inviting them to
OL,14,Fthe State of the Union address.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772041213
OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"We're giving the State of the Union
OL,8,Fspeech on Tuesday night. I could send
OL,9,Fa military plane or something, if you
OL,10,Fwould like to. It's the coolest night.
OL,11,FIt's the biggest speech," the
OL,12,Fpresident - over a speakerphone held
OL,13,Fby FBI Director Patel in the locker
OL,14,Froom - said.
OL,16,FHis comments were met with cheers and
OL,17,Fshouts of "we're in".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@YO]yD@KOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
