OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHe then joked that he would also have
OL,13,Fto invite the women's team, who had
OL,14,Fwon their own gold three days
OL,15,Fbeforehand.
OL,17,F"I must tell you, we're gonna have to
OL,18,Fbring the women's team - you do know
OL,19,Fthat."
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@FO]
