OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FThe president said that if the women
OL,8,Fweren't invited, "I do believe I
OL,9,Fprobably would be impeached, OK?"
OL,11,FThe US president phoned the men's team
OL,12,Fafter their victory, and invited them
OL,13,Fto the State of the Union before
OL,14,Fjoking that he would have to invite
OL,15,Fthe women's team too
OL,17,FVideo credit: mike malloy45, Instagram
