OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FMembers of the team laughed, and the
OL,8,Fvideo of the phone call and the
OL,9,Fplayers' response prompted significant
OL,10,Fbacklash on social media.
OL,12,FIt is unclear whether the president
OL,13,Fcontacted the women's team directly
OL,14,Fafter their win.
OL,16,FWhat happened at the State of the
OL,17,FUnion address?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
