CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772041213
OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FThe hockey players, wearing their
OL,8,Fmedals and "USA" sweaters, drew a
OL,9,Fstanding ovation from everyone in the
OL,10,Fchamber.
OL,12,FTrump pointed to the Democratic side
OL,13,Fof the room and said: "That's the
OL,14,Ffirst time I've ever seen them get up."
OL,16,FThe president also announced he would
OL,17,Fbe awarding the Presidential Medal of
OL,18,FFreedom, America's highest civilian
OL,19,Fhonour, to the hockey team's
OL,20,Fgoaltender, Connor Hellebuyck, who
OL,21,Fstopped 41 shots in the winning game.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@PO]uD@WOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
