SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772041213
OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FTrump announced the women would be
OL,8,Fhonoured with a White House visit
OL,9,F"soon", and the men's players
OL,10,Fresponded with thumbs-up gestures.
OL,12,FWhere was the women's team?
OL,14,FThe women's team declined their
OL,15,Finvitation because of scheduling
OL,16,Fissues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
