CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772041213
OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"We are sincerely grateful for the
OL,8,Finvitation extended to our gold medal-
OL,9,Fwinning U.S. Women's Hockey Team and
OL,10,Fdeeply appreciate the recognition of
OL,11,Ftheir extraordinary achievement," the
OL,12,Fteam spokesperson said in a statement.
OL,14,F"Due to the timing and previously
OL,15,Fscheduled academic and professional
OL,16,Fcommitments following the Games, the
OL,17,Fathletes are unable to participate.
OL,18,FThey were honored to be included and
OL,19,Fare grateful for the acknowledgment."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@aO]vD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
