OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FThe women's team was among the Olympic
OL,8,Fteams to visit the White House in
OL,9,FApril 2018.
OL,11,FThe team did receive alternative party
OL,12,Finvites following their victory,
OL,13,Fincluding from American rapper and TV
OL,14,Fpersonality Flavor Flav, who wrote on
OL,15,FInstagram: "If the USA Women's Hockey
OL,16,Fteam wants a real celebration and
OL,17,Finvite ... I'll host them in Las Vegas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772041213
OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"Do some nice dinners and shows and
OL,8,Fgood times. I'm sure I can get a hotel
OL,9,Fand airline to help me out here and
OL,10,Fcelebrate these women for real."
OL,12,FHow did the men's team react to the
OL,13,Fbacklash?
OL,15,FJack Hughes, who scored the overtime
OL,16,Fgoal that gave the team its win, said
OL,17,Fthe men are "tight" with the women's
OL,18,Fteam and said "everything is so
OL,19,Fpolitical".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
