CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772041213
OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Daily Mail on Monday,
OL,8,FHughes said: "We're so proud to
OL,9,Frepresent the US and when you get the
OL,10,Fchance to go to White House and meet
OL,11,Fthe president, we're proud to be
OL,12,FAmericans and that's so patriotic.
OL,14,F"No matter what your views are, we're
OL,15,Fsuper excited to go to the White House
OL,16,Ftomorrow and be a part of that."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
