OL,3,CHow locker room chat became
OL,4,Ccontroversial for the US men's hockey
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"People are so negative about things.
OL,8,FI think everyone in that locker room
OL,9,Fknows how much we support them, how
OL,10,Fproud we are of them and we know the
OL,11,Fsame way we feel about them, they feel
OL,12,Fabout us," he added.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
